      },
      {
      title: "What is a YAML file?",
      description: "YAML files are in the form of a list of elements, often in the form of key-value pairs.",
      },
      {
        title: "How does this apply to a CI/CD Pipeline?",
        description: "The YAML file .",
      },
      {
        title: "Sources:",
        description: "https://opensource.com/article/21/6/what-config-files, https://blogs.perficient.com/2024/02/26/building-re-usable-pipeline-templates-in-github-actions-workflows/#:~:text=In%20GitHub%20the%20portal%20offers%20a%20similar%20secrets%20option:%20https://docs.github.com/en/actions/security%2Dguides/using%2Dsecrets%2Din%2Dgithub%2Dactions%23about%2Dsecrets",
